item_category: This Stormforce Onyx Gaming PC is powered by a 10th Gen Intel Core i5 processor. That paired with NVIDEA's GTX 2060 6GB Graphics card and 16GB of Corsair RAM this PC can handle graphically demanding games like GTA V with ease. Windows Home 10 is pre-installed and Dual Band Wi-Fi comes installed as standard to have you up and gaming in no time.
